observationText: The SK-MEL-266 cell line harbors a Q282* nonsense mutation in the NF1 gene, with 37% of cells showing this mutation.
The SK-MEL-266 cell line has a L161* nonsense mutation in the NF1 gene, present in 49% of cells.
The SK-MEL-266 cell line exhibits copy number loss across the entire NF1 gene locus on chromosome 17.
